 "title": "Revealing Secrets",
 "summary": "In the much-rebuilt Sandbar tavern in Plaxton City, an assortment of patrons -- among them Aerilaya, Annalise, Daana, the intelligence agent Drax, and Tarrin -- gather amid the dark wood panelling and battered booths of Caspar's infamous watering hole. Over drinks in the survivor of three rounds of destruction, hidden truths and confidences are drawn out between them. The character-driven scene turns on the quiet exchange of secrets among the Sandbar's clientele.",
